{"tid":2515500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Neway被呈請清盤 高院排期7月聆訊","createTime":"2021-05-04T04:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T04:57:10.000Z","uid":186431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45d237a21f3af39e8c906f8710695ada15f77446","tid":2515500,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:47:48.000Z","msg":"【#BF社會熱話】Neway被呈請清盤 高院排期7月聆訊<br />\n.<br />\n卡拉OK連鎖集團「Neway」，其關聯公司Neway Music Limited，遭香港卡拉歌曲版權聯盟有限公司呈請清盤，高等法院排期7月28日進行清盤聆訊。據司法機構資料，債權人為香港卡拉歌曲版權聯盟有限公司。<br />\n.<br />\n疫情持續，卡拉OK場所多次被勒令關閉。「Neway」發言人近日表示，前線和後勤員工由今個月起停薪留職，約500名員工受影響。他強調，公司在停業期間，有向員工發半薪，惟每月開支過千萬，形容停薪留職安排是「迫不得已」，公司未有大規模裁員安排。<br />\n.<br />\nText by BusinessFocus Editorial<br />\n.<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n急需大額現金週轉？新鴻基信貸提供無上限物業一按二按貸款額！<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3bJiRKr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bJiRKr&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGniq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=6a43ed53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3bJiRKr</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n了解更多最快最新的財經、商業及創科資訊，請追蹤<br />\nInstagram:<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/businessfocus.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbusinessfocus.io%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGniq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=1206e900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/businessfocus.io/</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n時刻接收市場最新資訊，請追蹤Telegram頻道：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/businessfocusofficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbusinessfocusofficial&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGniq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=9bc0b5d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/businessfocusofficial</a